org.apache.hadoop.hbase

Class TestCustomPriorityRpcControllerFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.TestCustomPriorityRpcControllerFactory

  • public class TestCustomPriorityRpcControllerFactory
extends Object
    Tests that one can implement their own RpcControllerFactory and expect it to successfully pass custom priority values to the server for all HTable calls.
